article-mode is a minor (formerly major) mode that helps writing articles from a marketers view. It focuses on the specified keywords and their densities which are displayed in a separate window continuously.

<pre>
# Words      : (6125)
# Keywords   : 22
Density      : 0.36%
Keywords     : (emacs)
</pre>

You can get the latest code from http://www.timepoorblogger.com/files/article-mode.el.

Author Brian Gardner regularly posts enhancements and updates on article-mode to [http://www.timepoorblogger.com/ his blog].
